snippet.title: Nothing BETTER than starting your day with a GOOD LAUGH! - Best of KIDS and BABIES :)
snippet.description:
The funniest is yet to come! We do our best to fulfill your laughy expectations, we simply want to make your day better and funnier in any kind of ways :D Mixture of best fail collection with kids and babies in main role! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
